**FY_TUNNELS_SOURCE**

Created By MunkyheaD (alias MHead) 18/01/2011

Intro:
=======

Terrorists have taken over a factory which contains several secret information about political and environment issues.
S.W.A.T just arrived on time to kill each of the wrongdoers mercilessly. All of them have recently escaped from a federal 
prison.

TERRORISTS:
============

- Defend the factory and kill all CTU agents.

COUNTER-TERRORISTS:
====================

- Kill all terrorists and recover all missing information about the political and environment issues that has been stolen.

Tip:
======

If you want to "camp", this is not a map for this. The "SKULL" marks the point that you can't camp...UNDER NO CIRCUMSTANCES!!!
(By the way, only once for round)
